      "title": "8,179 dengue patients in June",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "In June alone, 8,179 dengue patients were reported, according to Dr. Sudath Samaraweera, director of the National Dengue Control Unit.",
        "So far this year, 32,385 dengue patients have been identified, he said, adding that a special dengue eradication program was launched in the Upper Province last week."
      ],
